Name: Murder, She Baked: Just Desserts
Title: Murder, She Baked: Just Desserts
Desc: Hannah (Alison Sweeney) investigates the murder of a fellow bake-off judge.
LongDescription: Hannah Swensen is thrilled when she is chosen as a guest for the first Eden Lake Dessert Bake-Off, but when fellow judge, coach Boyd Watson is found murdered, Hannah takes it upon herself to find the killer.
